Instruction
Use SVG icon for plus/minus icon
Create global typography class if needed.
Skip font-family, but must match colors and other typography attributes.
Smooth animation is required.
An only a single item can be opened at same time.
Installation
Fork a Codepen template and start editing using Codepen
